            "free_txt": [
              " The radioactivity produced in each foil was",
              "measured non-destructively using a high purity",
              "germanium (HPGe) gamma-ray detector GEM20-P,ORTEC.",
              "All samples were counted directly on the surface of",
              "the detector. In foil was also counted at 10 cm",
              "from the detector surface. The obtained 115m-In",
              "activity at 10 cm was considered as standard value to",
              "determine the detector efficiency for the extended",
              "sample on the surface.The gamma-ray spectrum was",
              "analyzed by GammaVision software. The efficiency vs.",
              "energy curve of the HPGe detector was determined using",
              "the standard point sources 57Co, 60Co, 133Ba and 152Eu.",
              "The efficiency for an extended sample (dia. 1.5 cm) on",
              "the surface of the detector was found to be 7.5% lower",
              "than that for a point source."
